<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Tue, 27 Jun 2023 21:14:11 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Nintendo says it'll be easy to transfer over to its next console]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>任天堂因其在线基础设施而名声不佳，经常被嘲笑<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-09-18-nintendo-switch-online-live-cloud-saves-broken.html">落后</a></ins>采用最新的技术或功能（例如<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2017-07-20-nintendos-solution-for-online-voice-chat-feels-half-baked.html">需要智能手机</a></ins>用于语音聊天）。这包括在旧控制台和新控制台之间转换用户数据。幸运的是，听起来任天堂至少正在考虑在推出下一款游戏机之前让这一切变得更容易。</p><p>在一个<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2023/qa2306.pdf">股东大会</a></ins>上周晚些时候，当被问及您购买的 Nintendo Switch 是否会延续到未来的游戏机时，总裁兼首席执行官 Shuntaro Furukawa 表示（通过谷歌翻译）：“在从 Nintendo Switch 到下一代游戏机的过渡中，我们希望让尽一切努力确保客户在使用任天堂帐户时能够顺利过渡。”这似乎意味着任天堂至少正在考虑允许通过 eShop 购买的当前 Nintendo Switch 游戏可以延续到接下来的任何游戏中。当然，任天堂不会对尚未公布的未来硬件发表评论，所以对此持保留态度。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>提醒一下，上一代<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://en-americas-support.nintendo.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/22282/~/can-i-transfer-games-from-older-systems-to-nintendo-switch%3F#:~:text=Nintendo%203DS%20and%20Wii%20U,games%20designed%20for%20other%20systems.">任天堂 Wii U 游戏并未移植到 Switch 上</a></ins>。这与索尼和微软形成鲜明对比，这两家公司的大多数上一代游戏机游戏都可以在新游戏机上运行。与微软和索尼不同的是，任天堂几乎喜欢在每一款新游戏机上为其控制器设计增添趣味。因此，有时不可能让游戏同时在新旧游戏机上运行。</p><p>至少，任天堂正在考虑对其未来的游戏机进行改进。以前拥有的游戏没有延续到新游戏机上，这一直是一个很大的失望，尤其是对于数字游戏购买者来说。当PlayStation 5可以玩时尤其令人气愤<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ps5-compatible-games-075940566.html">大多数 PlayStation 4 游戏</a></ins>，并且 Xbox Series S 和 X 可以玩<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/xbox-series-x-s-backward-compatibility-launch-day-142522349.html">大多数 Xbox One 游戏</a></ins>在某些情况下还包括 Xbox 360 游戏。就微软而言，该公司还允许您继承某些实体头衔。因此，任天堂在继承现有游戏方面有一些选择。无论任天堂的下一款游戏机是什么样，希望它能够与人们多年来积累的所有 Switch 游戏兼容。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/nintendo-says-itll-be-easy-to-transfer-over-to-its-next-console-211411270.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/nintendo-says-itll-be-easy-to-transfer-over-to-its-next-console-211411270.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> fae29689-4df3-45c4-8bb8-9b96a8070273</guid><dc:creator>曹彼得</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 21:14:11 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687900451</ingested><modified> 2023-06-27T21:14:18+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Game Consoles]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Peter Cao]]></category><media:content height="1067" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/be2a8a20-152b-11ee-bf27-53892d751f49" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1067" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/be2a8a20-152b-11ee-bf27-53892d751f49" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Kris Naudus / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Nintendo Switch and Switch OLED sitting atop a collection of games.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Nintendo Switch and Switch OLED]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best microSD cards in 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>如果您想为 Nintendo Switch、GoPro 或 Raspberry Pi 添加存储空间，您需要一张 microSD 卡。但是，虽然几张卡对于大多数用例来说<em>足够</em>快，但一些便宜的选项将比其他选项表现更好。为了帮助您找到可靠的存储增强器，我们最近对十几个 microSD 卡进行了一系列基准测试。</p><h2> microSD 卡需要注意什么</h2><h3>容量</h3><p>购买 microSD 卡时首先要弄清楚您需要多少空间。现代卡的容量通常为 32GB 到 512GB，少数也提供 1TB 型号。 2TB 卡理论上是可能的，但<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://petapixel.com/2022/09/30/kioxia-has-working-prototypes-of-the-worlds-first-2tb-microsd-card/">仍处于</a>原型阶段。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>对于大多数人来说，128GB 或 256GB 型号应该是价格和容量之间的最佳选择。但如果您需要更多空间（例如，在<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/steam-deck-review-small-hands-180026719.html">Steam Deck</a>上存放一堆游戏），512GB 卡可能更有意义，并且通常可以提供更好的每 GB 成本比。如今，你可以找到一张像样的 128GB 卡，价格大约为 15 美元或更少，一张像样的 256GB 卡，价格不到 30 美元，（<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://keepa.com/#!product/1-B09B1HMJ9Z">加上销售</a>）一张像样的 512GB 卡可能低至 40 美元（尽管大多数价格接近 50 或 60 美元）。当卡容量达到 1TB 时，价格上涨更为明显，通常价格约为 100 美元。</p><p>请注意，microSD 卡的性能可能会有所不同，具体取决于您购买的容量。 SanDisk 表示，其<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Western Digital;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=92bbc6e1-f32c-4060-9f86-b3358db79a39&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Western+Digital&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVLMWfp-vMvg_C-wQesY1U5IVOs6FMJfDrNv0N00SDEW&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westerndigital.com%2Fproducts%2Fmemory-cards%2Fsandisk-extreme-uhs-i-microsd%23SDSQXAA-128G-AN6MA">128GB Extreme 卡</a>可提供高达 90 MB/s 的连续写入速度，而同系列中更高容量的型号则可提供高达 130 MB/s 的速度。</p><p>今天我们谈论microSD卡时，通常指的是采用<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.sdcard.org/developers/sd-standard-overview/capacity-sd-sdhc-sdxc-sduc/">microSDXC（扩展容量）标准的</a>卡，其容量在32GB至2TB之间。您的设备需要支持此功能才能与 microSDXC 卡配合使用。如今，这几乎永远不会成为问题，但一些较旧的设备（例如<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://en-americas-support.nintendo.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/274/~/what-sd-cards-and-microsd-cards-are-compatible%3F">Nintendo 3DS</a> ）仅与 microSDHC（高容量）卡兼容，范围从 2GB 到 32GB。</p><h3>读写速度</h3><p>MicroSD 卡主要根据其读写速度进行评判，通常以兆字节每秒 (MB/s) 为单位进行衡量。一般来说，大多数 microSD 卡的读取速度比写入速度更快。然后可以将这些指标分解为顺序性能和随机性能。当您尝试访问或保存长时间、持续的数据流（例如打开大型视频或从 PC 复制大量文件）时，顺序读写速度很重要。如果你想使用microSD卡进行媒体存储，这一点尤为重要。</p><p>与此同时，随机性能是指卡读取和写入分散在设备中的小文件的速度。由于随机读/写速度远低于顺序读/写速度，因此存储设备制造商往往不会大声宣传它们。但如果您使用带有游戏设备或单板计算机（例如<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/raspberry-pi/">Raspberry Pi）</a>的卡，它们就很重要，因为它通常必须在随机位置快速保存和访问少量数据。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/a8a00b60-f034-11ed-bf3c-39241bbedf2b" alt="SD 协会的图表解释了其各种速度等级评级的工作原理。" data-uuid="95862b81-c662-36f2-8f52-1c7b363d1e5c"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> SD协会</div></figure><h3>速度等级</h3><p>如果您查看 microSD 卡，您会看到大量数字、字母和符号。其中大部分是指卡的<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.sdcard.org/developers/sd-standard-overview/speed-class/">速度等级</a>和性能等级，由<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.sdcard.org/">SD 协会</a>确定。</p><p>卡的视频速度等级或 V 等级详细说明了其最小顺序写入速度，这在从相机录制视频时尤其重要。其范围从V6到V90。我们测试的大多数卡都具有 V30 等级，因此它们的顺序写入速度至少为 30 MB/s。这应该足以支持较低比特率的 4K 视频。评级较高的 V60 和 V90 卡通常更适合捕获 8K，但它们的成本要高得多。</p><p> UHS 速度等级或 U 等级也指卡的最低顺序写入速度。它有两种类型：U3，要求至少 30 MB/s，U1，额定为 10 MB/s。</p><p>较旧的速度等级评级与其他两个系统重叠。它由 C 符号表示，从 2 级到 10 级，数字（再次）表示最小顺序写入速度。如今，该评级已不再那么重要，但您仍可能在某些卡上看到“C10”徽标。</p><p>应用程序性能规格以 A 符号标记，是随机读/写速度的指标。这是以 IOPS（每秒输入/输出操作数）而不是 MB/s 来衡量的。这里有两个类别：A1 卡提供 1,500 IOPS 的最低随机读取速度和 500 IOPS 的最低随机写入速度，而 A2 卡分别将这些速度提高到 4,000 IOPS 和 2,000 IOPS。这两个评级还保证顺序写入速度至少为 10 MB/s。</p><p>大多数人应该寻找具有 V30、U3 和 A2 等级的卡。完全有可能获得一张没有这些的固态卡：例如，如果您只需要一个具有高容量来保存文件的廉价选项，那么 U1 卡可能是值得的。如果您也认真拍摄高分辨率照片和视频，V60 和 V90 卡值得一看。但一般来说，具有上述认证的卡应该能够提供当今价格和性能的最佳组合。</p><p>需要强调的是，这些评级是基线。例如，许多 V30 卡的写入速度明显高于 30 MB/s，而某些 A1 卡在实践中的性能可能优于某些 A2 型号。制造商宣传的速度也并不总是 100% 准确：有时该卡在实际使用中会较慢，有时实际上可能会快一些。</p><h3> UHS 总线速度</h3><p>另一个需要注意的规格是该卡的总线接口。目前可用的大多数 microSD 卡都是 UHS-I，其理论最大速度为 104 MB/s。还有 UHS-II 卡，其背面有一排额外的引脚，最高可达 312 MB/s。 （也存在较新的 UHS-III 标准，但尚未得到广泛采用。）这些在卡上标有罗马数字 I 或 II。</p><p>目前绝对最快的 microSD 卡是 UHS-II 卡，它们通常具有 V60 或 V90 等级。如果您拍摄大量 4K 至 8K 视频或经常使用连拍模式拍摄超高分辨率照片，优质 UHS-II 卡的性能提升可以节省您的时间。</p><p>但这些卡比 UHS-I 卡贵得多：例如，ProGrade Digital 的这款<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:B&amp;H Photo;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=95276f3c-7b79-4c1e-803f-981cd9f7a968&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=B%26H+Photo&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAafiZn5xPHsbyBblZ1Bd0HcXB9uhTVUO7c7XnS6PL8P-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1560273-REG%2Fprograde_digital_pgmsd128gbpbh_128gb_microsdxc_uhs_ii_memory.html">128GB 型号的价格</a>相对便宜，价格为 55 美元。您还需要一个与 UHS-II 接口兼容的设备才能看到任何好处，当我们整理本指南时，UHS-II 卡的库存参差不齐。目前，对于绝大多数人来说，更高的速度并不值得付出溢价，因此我们大多坚持使用 UHS-I 选项。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-10/5b0bdf80-261b-11ec-93d7-3651390a7516" alt="Nintendo Switch 和 Nintendo Switch OLED，面朝下" data-uuid="a90e348a-e0aa-3056-ad4f-0f17f422a93e"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">克里斯·诺杜斯 / Engadget</div></figure><h3>关于读卡器、Nintendo Switch 和 Steam Deck 的说明</h3><p>虽然 UHS-I 规范的理论最大值为 104 MB/s，但某些 UHS-I 卡可以通过专有扩展超过该速度。不过，您需要兼容的读卡器和主机设备才能利用额外的性能。如果您发现 UHS-I 卡的广告速度高于 104 MB/s，则说明发生了这种情况。您可以在 Nintendo Switch 或 Steam Deck 上看到这些限制：<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.steamdeck.com/en/tech">这</a><a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://en-americas-support.nintendo.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/22481/~/microsd-card-faq">两种</a>游戏设备都支持 UHS-I 接口，并且不会超出其官方速度，从而使某些卡可能在其他地方获得的任何连续增益变得平坦。更广泛的结论是：您的 microSD 卡的速度只能与链条中最慢的一环一样快。</p><h3>保修单</h3><p>许多 microSD 卡经久耐用，可防水、耐极端温度、防 X 射线和防跌落。不过，如果发生灾难，长期保修总是好的。许多制造商提供终身有限保修，但我们注意到，销售的“耐用”卡可承受更长时间的书写，但保修时间通常要短得多。</p><h3>避免假货</h3><p>存储卡市场尤其存在销售假冒产品的骗子问题。为防止这种情况发生，请仅从知名品牌和信誉良好的零售商处购买，例如 Best Buy、B&amp;H Photo 或 Adorama。如果您在亚马逊<em>购物</em>，则仅当发货人和卖家是 Amazon.com 时才购买。 （尽管<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.reddit.com/r/NintendoSwitch/comments/dz3h6z/amazon_still_selling_fake_microsd_cards_even_if/">有少数用户报告说，</a>过去甚至直接从亚马逊收到过假货。）请记住：如果价格看起来好得令人难以置信，那么它很可能是真的。警惕任何提供明显低于其他价格的零售商。</p><p>收到卡后，请检查其包装是否有任何异常情况。您可以运行<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://crystalmark.info/en/">CrystalDiskMark</a>或<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2FwcHMuYXBwbGUuY29tL3VzL2FwcC9ibGFja21hZ2ljLWRpc2stc3BlZWQtdGVzdC9pZDQyNTI2NDU1MD9tdD0xMiIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjQxMWNhZGEtM2YxZS00ODdkLThkOWEtY2I1ZDMwYzE5ZmJhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAActngcAbGFJX7nyX4-HIJ1_WXXD3RN5G-OqiyGzawnQ0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fblackmagic-disk-speed-test%2Fid425264550%3Fmt%3D12">BlackMagic Disk Speed Test</a>等基准测试，以验证其速度不会大幅低于广告宣传的速度（或者可能的速度，考虑到其规格）。您还可以使用旨在验证卡的真实容量和性能的软件，例如<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://3ds.hacks.guide/h2testw-(windows).html">H2testw</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.majorgeeks.com/files/details/fakeflashtest.html">FakeFlashTest</a> 。</p><h2>我们如何测试</h2><p>我们对 12 张 microSD 卡进行了一系列测试，以验证其顺序和随机性能。其中包括<a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://crystalmark.info/en/">CrystalDiskMark</a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2FwcHMuYXBwbGUuY29tL3VzL2FwcC9ibGFja21hZ2ljLWRpc2stc3BlZWQtdGVzdC9pZDQyNTI2NDU1MD9tdD0xMiIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjQxMWNhZGEtM2YxZS00ODdkLThkOWEtY2I1ZDMwYzE5ZmJhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAActngcAbGFJX7nyX4-HIJ1_WXXD3RN5G-OqiyGzawnQ0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fblackmagic-disk-speed-test%2Fid425264550%3Fmt%3D12">BlackMagic Disk Speed Test</a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2FwcHMuYXBwbGUuY29tL3VzL2FwcC9hdHRvLWRpc2stYmVuY2htYXJrL2lkMTQ3OTEwMzY1OD9tdD0xMiIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjQxMWNhZGEtM2YxZS00ODdkLThkOWEtY2I1ZDMwYzE5ZmJhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAfoNsNSPZ5e0oF3_3GiMSNvT93g2ZShPtGye_0XhmWP9&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fatto-disk-benchmark%2Fid1479103658%3Fmt%3D12">ATTO Disk Benchmark</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.aja.com/products/aja-system-test">AJA System Test 等</a>基准测试，以及一些“真实世界”测试。我们在每张卡之间复制并粘贴一个大小约为 1.15GB 的照片小文件夹，然后对包含多种文件类型和子文件夹的较大 12.2GB 文件夹执行相同操作，并每次对过程进行计时。我们还检查了每张卡在 Steam Deck 上的表现，下载了不同大小的游戏，包括<a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N0b3JlLnN0ZWFtcG93ZXJlZC5jb20vYXBwLzQxMzE1MC9TdGFyZGV3X1ZhbGxleS8iLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY0MTFjYWRhLTNmMWUtNDg3ZC04ZDlhLWNiNWQzMGMxOWZiYSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAfF9kftCm_qY8ohWAxApv17c1uLn8DNN4rAY6XEWVx_O&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F413150%2FStardew_Valley%2F"><em>《星露谷物语》</em></a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N0b3JlLnN0ZWFtcG93ZXJlZC5jb20vYXBwLzE5MDI0OTAvQXBlcnR1cmVfRGVza19Kb2IvIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJmNDExY2FkYS0zZjFlLTQ4N2QtOGQ5YS1jYjVkMzBjMTlmYmEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAATgmruD8gtijYF0vpKXC9mtPTzhBAK0r5oyWRyVb-HeT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1902490%2FAperture_Desk_Job%2F"><em>《Aperture Desk Job</em></a> 》、 <a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N0b3JlLnN0ZWFtcG93ZXJlZC5jb20vYXBwLzIzNTQ2MC9NRVRBTF9HRUFSX1JJU0lOR19SRVZFTkdFQU5DRS8iLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY0MTFjYWRhLTNmMWUtNDg3ZC04ZDlhLWNiNWQzMGMxOWZiYSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAf-Fcoj7h56Iws3Ir1v0yzPVUTpWtUYsoV5Kd4wNOn-7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F235460%2FMETAL_GEAR_RISING_REVENGEANCE%2F"><em>《合金装备崛起：复仇》</em></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:25;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N0b3JlLnN0ZWFtcG93ZXJlZC5jb20vYXBwLzExNzI0NzAvQXBleF9MZWdlbmRzLyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjQxMWNhZGEtM2YxZS00ODdkLThkOWEtY2I1ZDMwYzE5ZmJhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAX6Dz1LiOG7XfZPyDoA4Mlv7wsLe_fKqHNgeGgTMOsM6&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1172470%2FApex_Legends%2F"><em>《Apex 英雄》</em></a> <em>&nbsp;</em> – 然后计算启动每个游戏和加载保存文件所需的时间。</p><p>我们使用<a data-i13n="cpos:26;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXTXomhyyqi9b591nnBxFTkj5m_dtJCoEERBZSexPB2g&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FKingston-MobileLite-Plus-UHS-II-Reader%2Fdp%2FB085P4Y1F1%2F">金士顿 USB 3.2 UHS-II 读卡器</a>在 Windows 11 和 macOS Ventura 上测试每张卡。对于前者，我们使用配备 Intel Core i9-10900F、Nvidia GeForce RTX 3080 GPU、32GB RAM 和 1TB SSD 的 Alienware <a data-i13n="cpos:27;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Dell;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=b1bb23c9-a2d4-4e4e-bfac-7a560ebe7641&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Dell&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZJl-bpdZeiHRWOQmAgmdgRnMdgbtlJeh52DNMpvZy5J&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dell.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Fgaming-and-games%2Falienware-aurora-r11-gaming-desktop%2Fspd%2Falienware-aurora-r11-desktop">游戏 PC</a> 。对于后者，我们使用了 2021 款 16 英寸 MacBook Pro，配备 Apple M1 Pro 芯片、16GB RAM 和 512GB SSD。为了在 MacBook 上使用我们的读卡器，我们使用了<a data-i13n="cpos:28;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Apple;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4130e2f0-a14f-4c5e-bdab-cd52ac7d8e79&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Apple&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATRypabjS61YXRZbRJGCCpl9MrHwAVFE0OZ1YzyO3mZs&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2FMUF82AM%2FA%2Fusb-c-digital-av-multiport-adapter">Apple 的 USB-C 数字 AV 多端口适配器</a>。</p><p>我们尽可能测试了每张卡的 128GB 版本，但对于几张卡（SanDisk Extreme 和 Samsung Pro Plus），我们只能测试其 256GB 型号。在使用 SD 协会的<a data-i13n="cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://www.sdcard.org/downloads/formatter/">存储卡格式化工具</a>进行测试之前，我们还重新格式化了每张卡。</p><h2>最适合大多数人：三星 Pro Plus</h2><p><core-commerce id="7fc8ee6462994ce2ac33fc1151b85a9b" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:30;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAYrW0O3VyHpgvgudrmz_rhohGSUCgYCGIVinHdXogG1e&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Fcomputing%2Fmemory-storage%2Fmemory-cards%2Fpro-plus-adapter-microsdxc-128gb-mb-md128sa-am%2F">三星 Pro Plus</a>提供了我们测试的卡中最好的顺序写入性能（CrystalDiskMark 中约为 130 MB/s），并且在随机读/写速度方面名列前茅，因此无论您购买的是相机、平板电脑或游戏掌上电脑。毫不奇怪，它具有所有必需的评级：U3、V30 和 A2。它的顺序读取性能不如我们下面的一些替代选择那么快，但也相差不远。例如，在我们的大文件传输测试中，它仅比最快的模型慢了四秒。</p><p> Pro Plus 128GB 的​​价格为 19 美元， <a data-i13n="cpos:31;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9TQU1TVU5HLW1pY3JvU0RYQy1FeHBhbmRlZC1NQi1NRDI1NktBLUFNL2RwL0IwQzFQUFdUV1Q_dGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby15aC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjQxMWNhZGEtM2YxZS00ODdkLThkOWEtY2I1ZDMwYzE5ZmJhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAeUHpdHB94O6M0T7QAJ0vNCS_-pIKvSjsUoiZuxBEBEC&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSAMSUNG-microSDXC-Expanded-MB-MD256KA-AM%2Fdp%2FB0C1PPWTWT%3Fth%3D1">256GB 的</a>价格为 30 美元， <a data-i13n="cpos:32;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9TQU1TVU5HLW1pY3JvU0RYQy1FeHBhbmRlZC1NQi1NRDI1NktBLUFNL2RwL0IwQzFQUllQWVg_dGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby15aC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjQxMWNhZGEtM2YxZS00ODdkLThkOWEtY2I1ZDMwYzE5ZmJhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAWqlkdmKfACno6wo6KzHSwksvn73fFfA98c5QMK3GWqm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSAMSUNG-microSDXC-Expanded-MB-MD256KA-AM%2Fdp%2FB0C1PRYPYX%3Fth%3D1">512GB 的</a>价格为 60 美元，因此它不是最便宜的选择，但仍然实惠。三星还销售<a data-i13n="cpos:33;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfojmjSel5Ych95bXj9Da2y7C7nqi3G4XL192vUAjWAp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Fcomputing%2Fmemory-storage%2Fmemory-cards%2Fpro-plus-reader-microsdxc-128gb-mb-md128sb-am%2F">带有 USB 读卡器的</a>卡，这将有助于它达到最大速度。无论哪种方式，它都享有 10 年有限保修。</p><p>如果您选择购买 Pro Plus，请确保购买三星于 2023 年 4 月<a data-i13n="cpos:34;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL25ld3Muc2Ftc3VuZy5jb20vdXMvc2Ftc3VuZy1hbm5vdW5jZXMtaW1wcm92ZWQtc3BlZWRzLXByby1wbHVzLW1lbW9yeS1jYXJkLWxpbmUtdXAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY0MTFjYWRhLTNmMWUtNDg3ZC04ZDlhLWNiNWQzMGMxOWZiYSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAcZUUJQWpatBLXxhD-YRCV4jWsq9GwxgjK-CcpVUWQWw&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.samsung.com%2Fus%2Fsamsung-announces-improved-speeds-pro-plus-memory-card-line-up">推出的</a>最新一代型号。目前，该公司仍在销售 Pro Plus 的上一代产品，它看起来相同，但并不相同。一样快，尤其是在随机读/写速度方面。 （寻找顺序读取速度额定为 180 MB/s 和顺序写入速度额定为 130 MB/s 的型号。）由于 128GB 型号的库存问题，我们测试了 256GB 版本的 Pro Plus，但这不应该对实际性能产生重大影响，因为三星对这两种卡的评级相同。</p><h2>亚军：金士顿 Canvas Go Plus</h2><p><core-commerce id="5a7ad9630b634097914b0d149c0bddf2" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果三星 Pro Plus 不可用或者您只是想省点钱， <a data-i13n="cpos:35;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZSQSyQdBu43qSKTfZ4nOCuQYkRi-DMV3jU59rFwlOC_&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0858MY6RT%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26psc%3D1">金士顿 Canvas Go Plus</a>是一个强有力的选择。它提供了我们在 CrystalDiskMark、ATTO 和 BlackMagic Disk Speed Test 测试中测试的所有卡中最高的顺序读取速度，仅略胜 SanDisk 的 Extreme 和 Nintendo Switch 品牌的卡。在我们的大文件传输测试中，它与这两张卡有效地结合在一起。它的顺序写入速度（在 CrystalDiskMark 上仅超过 100 MB/s）落后于 Pro Plus，但对于许多用途来说仍然足够快。它的随机读/写速度也仅次于三星的卡，因此它仍然是应用程序和游戏的不错选择。</p><p>这是一款 U3、V30 和 A2 级卡，并享有终身有限保修。 128GB 的​​价格为 17 美元， <a data-i13n="cpos:36;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDg1ODlSSzNNP3RoPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8teWgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY0MTFjYWRhLTNmMWUtNDg3ZC04ZDlhLWNiNWQzMGMxOWZiYSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdjdqVs519PAAsqpUScBJgm-SxHbXbl-EOTfz8aG_Pjj&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08589RK3M%3Fth%3D1">256GB</a>的价格通常不到 30 美元，它比 Pro Plus 稍便宜，并且与大多数具有此性能水平的卡一样实惠。不过，也有<a data-i13n="cpos:37;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAYPLDf9M3dnNfwVxInhTz5LpFUiJGS52QGIYC9_fK9Ed&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0858C71LT%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26th%3D1">512GB 型号</a>可供选择，但价格通常在 60 至 70 美元之间。到那时，您应该选择我们的替代选择之一（如果它们更便宜）。</p><h2>最超值：三星 Evo Select</h2><p><core-commerce id="63ab63a44e61408b8cd13b6bfc796dde" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:38;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAetja9D2j9e49xKjupP1bt33nvUFCpJ7wkrxhnRwSWaR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09B1JFY24%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26psc%3D1">三星 Evo Select</a>比我们的首选落后一步，特别是在顺序写入速度方面（CrystalDiskMark 上的速度略低于 70 MB/s），因此它不是相机的理想选择。尽管如此，它仍然可以完美满足许多需求，并且经常在亚马逊和三星的<a data-i13n="cpos:39;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAY_ttFpV8DFwwB8BSjPkeBQs383s4vIsNLGdlLYyEuA8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Fcomputing%2Fmemory-storage%2Fmemory-cards%2Fevo-select-adapter-microsdxc-128gb-mb-me128ka-am%2F">在线商店</a>以便宜的价格出售。过去，我们看到其 128GB、 <a data-i13n="cpos:40;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlCMUdYTTE2L3JlZj10d2lzdGVyX0IwOVE3UTJXWjE_X2VuY29kaW5nPVVURjgmcHNjPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8teWgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY0MTFjYWRhLTNmMWUtNDg3ZC04ZDlhLWNiNWQzMGMxOWZiYSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAWzsRTH5vQvmDQNRFO2FHxieDUveQILn2Zo7H3hN0MsV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09B1GXM16%2Fref%3Dtwister_B09Q7Q2WZ1%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26psc%3D1">256GB</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:41;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVR_hzDXmoP-1M_b_nrfLs2LRNH_7BWon2RZNMW0jFnq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSAMSUNG-microSDXC-Expanded-MB-ME256KA-AM%2Fdp%2FB09B1HMJ9Z%2F">512GB</a>型号的售价分别低至 12 美元、18 美元和 40 美元。尽管 Evo Select 具有更高的 V30、U3 和 A2 评级，但所有这些都与经常推荐的廉价卡<a data-i13n="cpos:42;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbTg-YTHgXfFtmFnNIblEuGqR5e8zrt1HFknQpf484_j&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0B7NTY2S6%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26th%3D1">SanDisk Ultra</a>相当。</p><p> Evo Select 的顺序读取速度与其宣传的峰值 130 MB/s 基本一致，这对许多人来说完全没问题。它的随机读/写性能明显落后于 Pro Plus 和 Canvas Go Plus，但与价格较高的存储卡（例如适用于 Nintendo Switch 的 SanDisk Extreme、Lexar Professional 1066x 和 SanDisk microSDXC）相当。与 Pro Plus 一样，它也享有 10 年保修。如果您只是想在一大块额外存储上节省几美元，那么这是一个很好的价值。</p><h2>另一个不错的选择：适用于 Nintendo Switch 的 SanDisk microSDXC 卡</h2><p><core-commerce id="272585d667724a7dbb425922e2a22a4a" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果您发现适用<a data-i13n="cpos:43;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhWNFo0VlJZLz90aD0xJnRhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLXloLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJmNDExY2FkYS0zZjFlLTQ4N2QtOGQ5YS1jYjVkMzBjMTlmYmEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAZZ6TVblclFG68ygqnFy-qJBI5ZEDsWWvEp7n_w6pf9K&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08V4Z4VRY%2F%3Fth%3D1">于 Nintendo Switch 的 SanDisk microSDXC 卡的</a>价格低于 Pro Plus 和 Canvas Go Plus，那么它是另一个值得选择的选择。在我们的基准测试中，它的顺序读取速度与金士顿卡大致相同，但其顺序写入速度稍慢（远远落后于 Pro Plus）。根据 CrystalDiskMark 的数据，它的随机读/写也落后了一步。该卡的 128GB 版本的价格通常比 Canvas Go Plus 稍高，但最近<a data-i13n="cpos:44;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhERzdGQjYxL3JlZj10d2lzdGVyX0IwQzNLWVZEV1Q_dGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby15aC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjQxMWNhZGEtM2YxZS00ODdkLThkOWEtY2I1ZDMwYzE5ZmJhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAdsoU1vMusq-NIbHhvqB3I7gbmQjqZrl97op8KpJiFXw&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08DG7FB61%2Fref%3Dtwister_B0C3KYVDWT%3Fth%3D1">512GB 版本的价格</a>已经降低了 10 美元左右。 SanDisk 还为该卡提供终身保修。请注意，我们测试了<em>Apex Legends</em>版本的 128GB 卡。 SanDisk 还销售一款<a data-i13n="cpos:45;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfuvNSDRSN61T42qx8gfcJ9ky5UP9YENcBaW5IEe01aZ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB07KXQX3S3%2Fref%3Dewc_pr_img_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26th%3D1"><em>超级马里奥</em>型号</a>，但我们无法透露该型号的性能如何。</p><h2>另一个不错的选择：Lexar Professional 1066x</h2><p><core-commerce id="c7b42cb1770849b59e6df97ec7bdd4c8" data-type="product-list"></p><p>同样，如果您想节省一点现金<a data-i13n="cpos:46;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhHR0NIS01ML3JlZj10d2lzdGVyX0IwQlRWTTdLNks_X2VuY29kaW5nPVVURjgmdGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby15aC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjQxMWNhZGEtM2YxZS00ODdkLThkOWEtY2I1ZDMwYzE5ZmJhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAY7URpY0KNBdNfO1V0aFLfBy2xj6BvCY9XzyYdG_m_Ex&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08GGCHKML%2Fref%3Dtwister_B0BTVM7K6K%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26th%3D1">，Lexar Professional 1066x</a>是 Pro Plus 的不错替代品。这是另一款 V30、U3 和 A2 卡，与 Pro Plus 一样，在我们的基准测试中，其顺序写入速度比 Canvas Go Plus 和 SanDisk Switch 卡要快一些。这些写入速度不如 Pro Plus 快，并且其顺序读取落后于所有三张卡。随机读/写也落后于 Pro Plus 和 Canvas Go Plus，我们注意到它的速度峰值和下降在我们的文件传输测试中更加明显。不过，速度并不慢。</p><p>该卡的 128GB 和<a data-i13n="cpos:47;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhHR0NNVDJaL3JlZj10d2lzdGVyX0IwQlRWTTdLNks_X2VuY29kaW5nPVVURjgmdGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby15aC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjQxMWNhZGEtM2YxZS00ODdkLThkOWEtY2I1ZDMwYzE5ZmJhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAWA0b2s6As9IKuOwTo2dGKJYl1kx3N5_MkNgbw5nYigx&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08GGCMT2Z%2Fref%3Dtwister_B0BTVM7K6K%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26th%3D1">256GB 型号</a>通常售价分别为 17 美元和 22 美元。如果您想要比金士顿卡提供更好的写入速度，那么与 Pro Plus 相比，后者可能更划算。 1066x 还提供终身有限保修。</p><h2>其他著名的 microSD 卡</h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/38115180-f037-11ed-b9ff-371a217f9a97" alt="SanDisk Extreme 和 PNY Elite-X microSD 卡。" data-uuid="ceece318-0178-3bc0-a68d-be6ae7c181f0"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Jeff Dunn / Engadget</div></figure><p>我们自己没有使用它，但如果您愿意购买更强大的 UHS-II 卡，用于重型视频录制， <a data-i13n="cpos:48;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDdWNUQ4N0M3P3RoPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8teWgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY0MTFjYWRhLTNmMWUtNDg3ZC04ZDlhLWNiNWQzMGMxOWZiYSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAbcfpA4y9s-U9i5HE-ZvE4fZ7okhTPkq_vUKrWlslv5A&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB07V5D87C7%3Fth%3D1">Delkin Devices Power</a>已经在其他地方进行了<a data-i13n="cpos:49;pos:1" href="https://havecamerawilltravel.com/fastest-microsd-cards/">良好的测试</a>，并且应该提供比我们的卡快得多的顺序写入速度。上面选的。它是我们实际上能在库存中找到的少数 UHS-II 卡之一，但它的价格很高，起价为 55 美元，容量仅为 32GB。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:50;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:B&amp;H Photo;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=95276f3c-7b79-4c1e-803f-981cd9f7a968&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=B%26H+Photo&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAY7_EXQZFUQUzUjHks0oVsOmvFyKWnjtQWvbA_eWVUrW&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1692702-REG%2Fsandisk_sdsqxaa_128g_an6ma_128gb_extreme_uhs_i_microsd.html">SanDisk Extreme</a>在我们的一些顺序写入测试中与 Pro Plus 有效匹配，并提供与 Canvas Go Plus 相当的顺序读取，但这部分是因为我们只能保护该卡的 256GB 型号，该型号更高 -额定值高于 128GB 版本。它的随机性能也远远落后于三星和金士顿卡，而且通常成本更高。总体而言，最近大多数零售商的 Extreme 库存都比较不稳定。然而，如果您看到信誉良好的卖家在出售它，那么这是另一种优质选择。</p><p>与此同时， <a data-i13n="cpos:51;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Western Digital;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=92bbc6e1-f32c-4060-9f86-b3358db79a39&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Western+Digital&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARXoVmQcy_PgKUhXCekoXdgDs-C8duQS4wRPNV0kYmTL&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westerndigital.com%2Fproducts%2Fmemory-cards%2Fsandisk-extreme-pro-uhs-i-microsd%23SDSQXCD-128G-GN6MA">SanDisk Extreme Pro 的</a>额定速度甚至更高（高达 200 MB/s 的顺序读取），但截至撰写本文时，大多数值得信赖的零售商似乎都无法提供该产品。</p><p>在 CrystalDiskMark 中， <a data-i13n="cpos:52;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAaWDG_XP7aqt5Teb8HTtGJKRjEmauhU-xuutsPebK_E4&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPNY-Elite-X-Micro-128GB-Class%2Fdp%2FB07KNTXKL3">PNY Elite-X 的</a>随机读/写性能与 Pro Plus 和 Canvas Go Plus 相差不远，而且它通常价格便宜，但在我们的顺序测试中远远落后。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-microsd-card-130038282.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-microsd-card-130038282.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f411cada-3f1e-487d-8d9a-cb5d30c19fba</guid><dc:creator>杰夫·邓恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 20:20:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687897218</ingested><modified> 2023-06-27T20:20:28+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jeff Dunn]]></category><media:content height="1173" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/4f77aa60-f3eb-11ed-9d5f-fe3fdd8ad1ed" width="1953"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1173" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/4f77aa60-f3eb-11ed-9d5f-fe3fdd8ad1ed" width="1953"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Photo by Jeff Dunn / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A handful of the microSD cards we tested for our best microSD card buying guide, including the Samsung Evo Select, Samsung Pro Plus (2023), SanDisk microSDXC Card for Nintendo Switch, Kingston Select Plus, Kingston Canvas Go Plus, SanDisk Extreme, Lexar Professional 1066x, Samsung Pro Plus (2021), Samsung Pro Endurance, PNY XLR8 Gaming, PNY Elite-X and Kingston High Endurance.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[MicroSD cards]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Podcast app Stitcher is shutting down in August]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>缝合器正在关闭。根据其网站上的常见<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://stitcher.helpshift.com/hc/en/1-stitcher/faq/975-will-stitcher-continue-to-make-podcasts/">问题解答</a>（ <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://variety.com/2023/digital/news/stitcher-shutting-down-siriusxm-podcast-app-1235655994/">来自</a><em>Variety</em> ），SiriusXM <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/siriusxm-acquires-stitcher-podcasts-122816348.html">于 2020 年以 3.25 亿美元收购的</a><a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/stitcher-podcast-app-redesign-181302116.html">流行播客应用程序</a>和网络服务将于 8 月 29 日关闭。此举似乎是为了吸引其用户群进入更广泛的 SiriusXM 平台。</p><p> “Stitcher 的所有者 SiriusXM 致力于将播客纳入其旗舰 SiriusXM 订阅业务，”结账说明中写道。 “订阅者可以在 SiriusXM 应用程序中收听播客，并将在今年晚些时候看到全新的收听体验。”该通知补充说，Stitcher Studios 及其 Earwolf 喜剧网络将继续制作播客。尽管 Stitcher 表示其优质内容可能会在其他地方继续存在，但它补充说，“主持人/创作者将决定其节目的可用性和可访问性。”该公司建议在社交媒体上关注您最喜欢的播客创作者，以了解各个节目的命运。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>该平台一直是独家和跨平台播客的热门目的地。 Stitcher 的原创播客包括<em>Freakonomics Radio</em> 、Quentin Tarantino 和 Roger Avary 的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/quentin-tarantino-is-getting-his-own-film-podcast-on-stitcher-this-summer-191406422.html"><em>视频档案播客</em></a>、 <em>LeVar Burton Reads</em>和<em>Science Rules！与比尔·奈（Bill Nye）</em> （以及其他人）。该应用程序以其用户友好的导航、广泛的图书馆和发现建议而闻名。</p><p>该公司成立于 2008 年，是一家初创公司，专注于听力应用程序。Deezer 于 2014 年<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2014-10-24-deezer-buys-stitcher.html">收购了该公司</a>，并于两年后将<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2016-06-06-deezer-sells-stitcher-less-than-two-years-after-purchasing-it.html">其出售给 Midroll Media</a> 。最终，母公司 EW Scripps Company 在 2020 年将其出售给了 SiriusXM，但这家卫星广播提供商今天宣布关闭。</p><p> Stitcher 今天关闭了付费订阅的自动续订，并详细介绍了高级客户的退款流程。已有订阅的用户无需采取任何操作即可取消。与此同时，计划在 8 月 29 日之后续订年度订阅的用户将收到已付费年度未使用部分的按比例退款。 （您可以<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://stitcher.helpshift.com/hc/en/1-stitcher/faq/976-what-will-happen-to-my-stitcher-premium-paid-subscription/">在此处</a>阅读完整条款。）</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/podcast-app-stitcher-is-shutting-down-in-august-195644781.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/podcast-app-stitcher-is-shutting-down-in-august-195644781.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 38d48bb8-7941-4d8f-aa1a-7ba155b813ff</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 19:56:44 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687896967</ingested><modified> 2023-06-27T20:16:10+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Celebrities]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="1287" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/b4dd6170-1523-11ee-b7f9-217ed4d51bbf" width="2625"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1287" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/b4dd6170-1523-11ee-b7f9-217ed4d51bbf" width="2625"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Stitcher]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Three phones showing different views of the Stitcher podcast app in front of a blue background]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Stitcher]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Volvo is the latest automaker to adopt Tesla's EV charging standard in North America]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/rivian-owners-will-be-able-to-use-tesla-superchargers-starting-in-2024-141546633.html">采用特斯拉电动汽车充电技术的</a>不仅仅是美国制造商。沃尔沃已<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.media.volvocars.com/us/en-us/media/pressreleases/316416/electric-volvo-car-drivers-will-get-access-to-12000-tesla-superchargers-across-the-united-states-can">确认</a>其在美国、加拿大和墨西哥的电动汽车将使用特斯拉的北美充电标准（NACS）端口。从 2024 年上半年开始，当前和最近发布的汽车（例如<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/volvos-2022-c-40-recharge-adds-fastback-style-to-the-xc-40-150027300.html">C40 Recharge</a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/volvo-officially-unveils-the-ex30-its-compact-electric-suv-113500803.html">EX30</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/volvo-officially-reveals-the-ex90-ev-suv-its-safest-car-ever-144414196.html">EX90</a> ）将通过适配器连接到 Supercharger 站，而 2025 年以后的车型将内置 NACS。适配器将可用于使用组合充电系统（CCS）格式连接即将推出的电动汽车。</p><p>沃尔沃并不羞于表达自己的理由。它希望驾驶员能够使用“简单便捷”的充电网络，这意味着特斯拉超级充电站。该公司声称，这笔交易将使车主能够使用另外 12,000 个快速充电地点。沃尔沃汽车应用程序将帮助用户查找加油站并付费。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>此举使沃尔沃成为第一个使用特斯拉港口的欧洲品牌。它加入了实现这一飞跃的美国品牌行列，包括<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ford-ev-drivers-will-get-access-to-12000-north-american-tesla-superchargers-next-spring-221752191.html">福特</a>、 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gm-ev-owners-will-gain-access-to-tesla-superchargers-in-2024-002123436.html">通用汽车</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gm-ev-owners-will-gain-access-to-tesla-superchargers-in-2024-002123436.html">Rivian</a> 。这些公司还承诺为当前设计提供适配器，并随后提供本地 NACS 端口。</p><p>特斯拉于 2022 年底<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tesla-is-offering-its-proprietary-charge-connector-as-a-new-north-american-standard-193223322.html">开放了 NACS</a> ，让任何想要使用该技术的公司都可以使用该技术。当时，它希望 Chargepoint 和 Electrify America 等充电网络能够支持该系统。虽然这一目标尚未实现，但 NACS 正在迅速获得汽车制造商以外的支持。 <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/texas-says-state-funded-ev-charging-stations-need-to-include-teslas-nacs-connector-141517283.html">德克萨斯州将要求在国家资助的充电站上使用特斯拉的连接器</a>，SAE International 正在开发<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-sae-is-creating-a-standardized-version-of-teslas-ev-charging-plug-175233691.html">该插头的标准化版本</a>。</p><p>其他汽车巨头对于使用特斯拉的技术并不确定。 Stellantis（克莱斯勒、阿尔法罗密欧、菲亚特和其他品牌的所有者） <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-says-it-is-evaluating-teslas-charging-standard-2023-06-13/">告诉</a><em>路透社，</em>它正在“评估”NACS，而现代汽车也在<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hyundai-consider-joining-teslas-north-american-charging-standard-alliance-2023-06-20/">考虑</a>采用。切换并不一定容易。现代和保时捷等制造商拥有 800 伏架构，可以比现有的超级充电器更快地充电，他们要么必须向特斯拉施压，要求升级技术，要么接受不太理想的充电速率。尽管如此，接受特斯拉模式的压力显然越来越大。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/volvo-is-the-latest-automaker-to-adopt-teslas-ev-charging-standard-191942675.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/volvo-is-the-latest-automaker-to-adopt-teslas-ev-charging-standard-191942675.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 5d06c940-e38a-41cd-9339-260ad1dd04e0</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 19:19:42 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687894686</ingested><modified> 2023-06-27T19:38:11+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[Autos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[Environment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Nature & Environment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/10437260-151b-11ee-9d57-9d30043e4776" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/10437260-151b-11ee-9d57-9d30043e4776" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Volvo]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Volvo EX90]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Volvo EX90]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best gaming handhelds in 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>手持游戏系统正在风靡一时。是的，自 Game Boy 诞生以来，随时随地玩游戏就已经成为一种潮流，但 Nintendo Switch 的巨大成功和移动处理器的持续增长带来了设备的爆炸式增长，让您可以随时随地玩各种游戏。然而，找出最适合您的游戏掌上电脑可能很复杂。您已经知道 Switch 值得购买，但根据您想要玩的游戏，合适的掌机可能花费您不到 100 美元或接近 1,000 美元。为了帮助您缩小范围，我们广泛研究了最好的手持游戏机，并测试了主要的竞争者，从强大的便携式电脑到紧凑的仿真机。</p><h2>关于游戏掌上电脑市场需要了解什么</h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/b56e1aa0-fa46-11ed-bf6c-fd19d876366a" alt="木制桌面上放置着一系列游戏手持设备。这些手持设备包括 Nintendo Switch - OLED 型号、Valve Steam Deck 和 Retroid Pocket 3，以及连接到 Backbone One 移动游戏控制器的 iPhone 12 mini。" data-uuid="e139d903-acea-3db5-a68c-043cb5ca49cd"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">杰夫·邓恩 / Engadget</div></figure><p>游戏手持设备市场可分为三个主要层次。在顶部，您有基于 x86 的便携式游戏 PC，例如<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/steam-deck-review-small-hands-180026719.html">Steam Deck</a>或<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/asus-rog-ally-hands-on-possibly-the-most-powerful-handheld-gaming-pc-yet-140054506.html">Asus ROG Ally</a> 。这些是您可以购买的最强大的手持设备，因为它们试图复制中等规格游戏台式机的体验。 Steam Deck 在 Linux 上运行，但大多数其他人使用 Windows。如果您想随时随地玩最近发布的现代 PC 游戏（并且需要比 Switch 更强大的设备），那么这就是您需要的设备类型。它们还可以模拟最广泛的复古游戏机。然而，它们通常是最大、最笨重的设备，而且电池寿命可能很短。当然，它们也是最昂贵的，价格从 400 美元到 1,000 多美元不等。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>价格范围内进一步下降的是移动手持设备，例如<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/logitech-g-cloud-gaming-handheld-preorder-amazon-logi-play-142636818.html">Logitech G Cloud</a>或<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/retroid-pocket-3-irl-153508438.html">Retroid Pocket</a> 。它们通常运行 Android 或 Linux，价格从 50 美元到 400 美元左右不等。它们无法玩现代游戏机或 PC 游戏，但它们通常比便携式 PC 更紧凑，并且仍然可以用于移动游戏和云流媒体。虽然大多数产品都是为了这些目的而营销的，但许多游戏玩家实际上购买它们是为了通过像<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.retroarch.com/">RetroArch</a>这样的软件来模拟视频经典游戏。让模拟器工作<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://retrogamecorps.com/2022/01/16/retroid-pocket-2-starter-guide/">可能很复杂</a>，并且以这种方式访问​​玩游戏所需的 BIOS 和 ROM 文件在<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.howtogeek.com/262758/is-downloading-retro-video-game-roms-ever-legal/">法律上也很模糊</a>。 （Engadget 不纵容盗版。不过，备份您已拥有的游戏文件仅供个人使用被认为更具防御性，因此移动手持设备可以成为一种对用户和钱包更友好的方式来随时随地玩经典游戏.) 如今，顶级移动手持设备中的 ARM 芯片可以将游戏模拟到<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sixth_generation_of_video_game_consoles">第六代</a>游戏机中。</p><p>我们将最后一层称为“做自己事情的手持设备”。这是对<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nintendo-switch-oled-review-130025998.html">Switch</a>或<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/playdate-review-indie-games-crank-170054294.html">Playdate</a>等设备的统称：运行高度定制的软件并旨在提供独特的游戏体验的便携式设备。它们不一定适合模拟或玩最新的多平台游戏；相反，他们通常拥有不同的游戏库。因此，它们可能不会具有最广泛的吸引力（Switch 除外），但对于不太懂技术的人来说，它们通常更容易上手和使用。</p><h2>最适合大多数人的手持游戏电脑：Valve Steam Deck</h2><p><core-commerce id="5ca7e3ede9464a9a8dff8eb0f10a91ff" data-type="product-list"></p><p>在过去的一年里<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N0b3JlLnN0ZWFtcG93ZXJlZC5jb20vc3RlYW1kZWNrIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkZmMzZTBiMy1kYTIxLTQxZTYtYjRjOC0wZmNjNDExZTg2ZGQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAWaWEBDFIbCkCQSBymrLEUKQlUVVwWEAkJd3QFK6BA01&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fsteamdeck">，Valve 的 Steam Deck</a>已经得到了充分的记录，但它仍然在游戏手持设备市场上提供了价格和功能的最佳平衡。具体来说，我们谈论的是入门级型号，售价 399 美元，配备 64GB eMMC 存储（可以<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-microsd-card-130038282.html">使用 microSD 卡</a>轻松扩展）。配备更快 SSD 的 529 美元和 649 美元型号以及最高端型号的优质玻璃显示屏也非常棒，但一些新的 Windows 手持游戏设备可能会削弱其价值主张，至少对某些人来说是这样。 （我们将在下面深入探讨这一点。）</p><p>尽管如此，入门级 Steam Deck 仍然是一款功能非常强大的设备。虽然 Steam 库中的每款游戏都与设备的基于 Linux 的操作系统兼容，但已有数千款游戏兼容，而且<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.steamdeck.com/en/verified">经过官方验证</a>且<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.protondb.com/">仍可玩的</a>游戏列表一直在增长。它可以原生稳定地玩一些在 Nintendo Switch 上无法玩的游戏，从<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/elden-ring/"><em>《Elden Ring》</em></a>到<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/final-fantasy-7-remake-review-120044800.html"><em>《最终幻想 VII 重制版》</em></a>再到《 <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/resident-evil-4-review-a-half-step-backward-for-capcom-remakes-070100973.html"><em>生化危机 4</em>重制版》</a> 。这个过程并不像任天堂的游戏机那样即插即用，因为一些游戏需要调整才能以最佳方式运行，而一些较新的 AAA 游戏已经<a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.eurogamer.net/digitalfoundry-2023-can-steam-deck-handle-a-range-of-pcs-most-challenging-games">开始突破</a>设备的极限。但 SteamOS 使其设置相对容易访问，实际上，这本质上是一款以 720p 播放但可以随身携带的上一代游戏机。</p><p>这种强大的功能也使 Steam Deck 成为出色的仿真设备。虽然有些系统需要一些调整（Wii），而另一些系统则更依赖于游戏（通常很棘手的 PS3 和 Xbox），但大多数系统都可以完美运行，并且几乎所有内容都至少可以玩。甚至可以玩更高端的Switch游戏。使用<a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.emudeck.com/">EmuDeck</a>这样的工具也可以使所有这些设置变得尽可能简单。除了仿真之外，Deck 的灵活性使其成为<a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Microsoft;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=67071605-d4df-494e-8d9c-c9c236b8bb38&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Microsoft&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAemyVIYPRQhYQLgTCnHT_d_Vx7XFCDrx82Z0rDEpelPS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Ftopic%2Fxbox-cloud-gaming-in-microsoft-edge-with-steam-deck-43dd011b-0ce8-4810-8302-965be6d53296">云流 Xbox 游戏</a>的优秀设备。您还可以将其<a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9KU0FVWC1Db21wYXRpYmxlLURpc3BsYXlQb3J0LUV0aGVybmV0LURlY2stSEIwNzAyL2RwL0IwQkpLQlMxUVM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tenItMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImRmYzNlMGIzLWRhMjEtNDFlNi1iNGM4LTBmY2M0MTFlODZkZCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAeO33cdnR9uoyy8AlH9uZcJU84VuDD60G3y1E_2FisX7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FJSAUX-Compatible-DisplayPort-Ethernet-Deck-HB0702%2Fdp%2FB0BJKBS1QS">与扩展坞</a>配对，并在电视或显示器上以更高分辨率玩许多（但不是全部）游戏。</p><p> Steam Deck 最大的缺陷是它的尺寸：重 1.5 磅，厚约两英寸，长不到一英尺，它突破了“手持”设备的极限。即使你的手很大，握住几个小时也会很累。根据您玩的游戏，其电池续航时间从八小时到不到两个小时不等。 7 英寸 IPS LCD 显示屏虽然不错，但不如 Switch OLED 那样充满活力，而且方向键也有些糊状。话虽如此，Deck 是一套坚固的套件。它的操纵杆非常光滑，正面按钮和触发器反应灵敏，散热舒适。它与使用普通控制器的感觉并不遥远​​，此外还有四个可自定义的后退按钮和两个触控板，使 PC 风格的游戏 UI 导航更加容易。虽然整个东西很重，但它的轮廓手柄可以自然地滑入手中。您可以阅读我们完整的<a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/steam-deck-review-small-hands-180026719.html">Steam Deck 评论</a>以了解更多详细信息。</p><h2>关于更强大的 Steam Deck 替代品的说明</h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/6c0fdd50-f012-11ed-9dfe-3604a98145d7" alt="华硕 ROG 盟友" data-uuid="4a4f024d-34ea-3eb1-98a7-4ce97d10e6f8"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Sam Rutherford/Engadget</div></figure><p>拥有 Steam 可以让 Valve 降低大多数手持电脑的价格，因此入门级 Steam Deck 仍将保持 399 美元的杀手级价格。不过，如果您的预算较高并且想要技术最先进的手持设备，那么有一些基于 Windows 的设备可能值得考虑。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=5e0bed65-d2f8-4b34-9b8f-955218c0e37a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Best+Buy&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAX3lhzhPY6Ol0HOWrebawl2RMpUu2xcrSY8tKdtvOQbN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bestbuy.com%2Fsite%2Fasus-rog-ally-7-120hz-fhd-1080p-gaming-handheld-amd-z1-extreme-processor-512gb-white%2F6542964.p%3FskuId%3D6542964&amp;uuid=DVJCldqJwtehCogz25656">华硕 ROG Ally</a>是其中最引人注目的。它运行在更新的 AMD 芯片上，理论上可以以更高的帧速率玩要求更高的游戏。它的 7 英寸显示屏比 Deck 具有更高的分辨率 (1080p) 和更快的刷新率 (120Hz)，它更小、更轻， <a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/asus-rog-ally-handheld-gaming-pc-starts-at-600-164810578.html">最终的起价将是</a>相对合理的 600 美元。<a data-i13n="cpos:26;pos:1" href="https://www.pcmag.com/reviews/asus-rog-ally">其他</a><a data-i13n="cpos:27;pos:1" href="https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2023/05/the-asus-rog-ally-runs-windows-eats-battery-and-needs-time-to-cook/">网站</a><a data-i13n="cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://www.tomshardware.com/reviews/asus-rog-ally-ryzen-z1-extreme">的</a>评论说确实更强大。由于它来自成熟的制造商，因此可以在<a data-i13n="cpos:28;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Best Buy;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=5e0bed65-d2f8-4b34-9b8f-955218c0e37a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Best+Buy&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdPDqHHxxS-NLP_szrHJO9EqlXraLzmoi-JViMZmHsrl&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bestbuy.com%2Fsite%2Fasus-rog-ally-7-120hz-fhd-1080p-gaming-handheld-amd-ryzen-z1-extreme-processor-512gb-white%2F6542964.p%3FskuId%3D6542964">百思买的</a>主要零售商处购买。 It comes in two variants: The model with a Ryzen Z1 Extreme CPU costs <a data-i13n="cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=5e0bed65-d2f8-4b34-9b8f-955218c0e37a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Best+Buy&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAX3lhzhPY6Ol0HOWrebawl2RMpUu2xcrSY8tKdtvOQbN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bestbuy.com%2Fsite%2Fasus-rog-ally-7-120hz-fhd-1080p-gaming-handheld-amd-z1-extreme-processor-512gb-white%2F6542964.p%3FskuId%3D6542964&amp;uuid=QyPfkVT8gqJftBqX27656">$700</a> and is out now, while a lower-end configuration is expected sometime in Q3 2023. We&#39;re still in the process of reviewing the ROG Ally but will have a more complete verdict in the near future.</p><p> The ROG Ally and other notable new handhelds like the <a data-i13n="cpos:30;pos:1" href="https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/ayaneo-2s-fully-upgraded-amd-7840u-handheld/coming_soon">Ayaneo 2S</a> run on Windows 11, so they can play games from clients like Epic, GOG, <a data-i13n="cpos:31;pos:1" href="http://itch.io/">Itch.io</a> and the Xbox app instead of just Steam. Yes, it&#39;s <a data-i13n="cpos:32;pos:1" href="https://www.google.com/search?q=how+to+play+epic+games+gog+on+steam+deck+engadget&amp;rlz=1C1CHBF_enUS924US924&amp;oq=how+to+play+epic+games+gog+on+steam+deck+engadget&amp;aqs=chrome..69i57.5670j0j7&amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;ie=UTF-8">technically possible</a> to play non-Steam games on SteamOS, but that&#39;s not the point of the Deck. And while Valve is doing an admirable job of getting more Windows games working on a Linux-based OS, it&#39;s still running a layer. Every now and then, an update will break something in a given game.</p><p> But Windows certainly isn&#39;t immune to things going haywire, and so far, no Windows handheld has really nailed a portable UI as well as the Steam Deck. Battery life can be shorter, too. The consensus on the ROG Ally seems to be that these are still issues there. Plus, even <a data-i13n="cpos:33;pos:1" href="https://www.theverge.com/23719210/asus-rog-ally-review">after updates</a> , the performance jump may not always be massive by default. The Ally&#39;s gains over the Deck <a data-i13n="cpos:34;pos:1" href="https://www.eurogamer.net/digitalfoundry-2023-asus-rog-ally-vs-steam-deck-review">appear to be</a> most notable at higher power modes, but running at a higher wattage (and a higher resolution) also means nuking the battery. Still, it should be faster when all else is equal.</p><p> Of the Windows handhelds we&#39;ve reviewed, we&#39;ve found the <a data-i13n="cpos:35;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ayaneo-2-review-specs-price-a-more-premium-and-pricier-take-on-the-steam-deck-143039617.html">Ayaneo 2</a> and <a data-i13n="cpos:36;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ayaneo-air-plus-mini-steam-deck-163047036.html">Ayaneo Air Plus</a> to be competent alternatives to the Steam Deck with generally higher performance. The <a data-i13n="cpos:37;pos:1" href="https://gpd.hk/gpdwin4">GPD Win 4</a> is relatively well-regarded, too. But the software experience on these devices isn&#39;t nearly as optimized as SteamOS, and devices with better hardware are now arriving. We&#39;ll update this guide once we&#39;re able to review the ROG Ally, Ayaneo 2S or other handhelds with a Ryzen 7000 series chip.</p><h2> Best budget handheld gaming system: Retroid Pocket 3+</h2><p><core-commerce id="a2d0186f0f49446e987f80ea348ba257" data-type="product-list"></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:38;pos:1" href="https://www.goretroid.com/collections/retro-game-system/products/retroid-pocket-3-handheld-retro-gaming-system-1">Retroid Pocket 3+</a> is an Android device with far less power than the Steam Deck or portable Windows PC, so the only way it can play modern games is via cloud streaming. But if you primarily want a handheld to emulate older games when you&#39;re away from your home console or gaming PC, this is a generally comfortable and, at $149, reasonably affordable way to do so.</p><p> We <a data-i13n="cpos:39;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/retroid-pocket-3-irl-153508438.html">praised this handheld&#39;s predecessor</a> , the Pocket 3, in 2022. The Pocket 3+ is effectively the same device, but with a stronger chipset (the Unisoc T618) and more RAM (4GB). The design is like a smaller Nintendo Switch Lite, which is to say it&#39;s slim, lightweight (235g) and fairly ergonomic, so it&#39;s not fatiguing for long gaming sessions. The 4.7-inch touch display isn&#39;t huge, but it&#39;s bright and saturated, with a sharp-enough 750 x 1,334 resolution and a 16:9 aspect ratio that plays nice for cloud streaming and emulating systems like the PSP. (You&#39;ll get borders with some older consoles, though.) The hardware still has some quirks: The face buttons are on the beady side, the start and select buttons are oddly placed on the left-hand side and the analog triggers aren&#39;t pressure-sensitive. The joysticks are on the shallower side, too, though they&#39;re smooth and accurate in action. For the money, the Pocket 3+ is built well and easy to transport.</p><p> The Pocket 3+ can emulate consoles up to the Dreamcast/PSP range fairly comfortably, so you&#39;ll have few troubles if you&#39;re mainly looking to play older games from the SNES, PS1 and earlier. With a recent <a data-i13n="cpos:40;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:YouTube;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=89f68c82-f255-44fa-8db9-03fec996b93a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=YouTube&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI4OWY2OGM4Mi1mMjU1LTQ0ZmEtOGRiOS0wM2ZlYzk5NmI5M2EiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueW91dHViZS5jb20vd2F0Y2g_dj1vMnl3ZjNwMW1zRSIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZGZjM2UwYjMtZGEyMS00MWU2LWI0YzgtMGZjYzQxMWU4NmRkIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAZFWxaxpabXLF9uZlUNJgAzn0xzs6TO89QC6fM10O_6x&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do2ywf3p1msE">firmware update</a> , the device&#39;s performance has also improved with more demanding machines like the PlayStation 2 and GameCube. It&#39;s still not flawless (particularly with the PS2), but numerous games are at least playable, which is impressive at this price. You can also play most native Android games or stream games from a PC, Xbox or PS5. Battery life will depend on what you&#39;re playing but typically lasts between five and seven hours.</p><p> Retroid recently launched a handheld called the <a data-i13n="cpos:41;pos:1" href="https://www.goretroid.com/collections/retro-game-system/products/retroid-pocket-flip">Pocket Flip</a> that&#39;s more or less the Pocket 3+ with a clamshell design. It costs $10 more and uses sliders instead of joysticks, but if you&#39;d prefer a form factor that&#39;s closer to a Nintendo DS than a Switch Lite, feel free to get that instead.</p><h2> A more powerful Android option: AYN Odin</h2><p><core-commerce id="d0d27a65b50c41749a9d40d7e2095861" data-type="product-list"></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:42;pos:1" href="https://www.ayntec.com/collections/odin">AYN Odin</a> is worth considering if you like the idea of the Retroid Pocket 3+ but are willing to pay a little more for better emulation performance with systems like the GameCube, PS2 and Wii. Its Snapdragon 845 processor and Adreno 635 GPU still can&#39;t run 100 percent of games from those systems, but the Odin <a data-i13n="cpos:43;pos:1" href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zATLq_UshE1Nw6HhHuJvrv6f6xFyK8nHrUdDd6bO7KM/edit#gid=1678734171">can do more</a> than the Pocket 3+, and the handful that are playable on both devices will generally perform better here. The device is even capable of <a data-i13n="cpos:44;pos:1" href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zATLq_UshE1Nw6HhHuJvrv6f6xFyK8nHrUdDd6bO7KM/edit#gid=1022148806">playing some</a> 3DS games.</p><p> The Odin is also a better piece of hardware than the Pocket 3+. Its layout is pretty much the same, but it has gentle curves on the back that make it easier to grip, a couple of customizable back buttons and analog triggers that&#39;ll play nicer with more modern games and cloud streaming. It has a larger 6-inch 1080p display, and it should still get around five to seven hours of battery life on average. It&#39;s not as portable as Retroid&#39;s handheld, but its build quality is more substantial on the whole.</p><p> All of this makes the Odin a better device than the Pocket 3+, but it&#39;s hard to call it a better value. AYN sells three different Odin models: The base version, which often goes for $240, is probably the “Goldilocks” option for most people. A more powerful Odin Pro comes with twice the RAM (8GB) and storage (128GB) but costs $290; at that price, you&#39;re getting pretty close to the Steam Deck, which is comprehensively superior. There&#39;s also the $200 <a data-i13n="cpos:45;pos:1" href="https://www.ayntec.com/collections/odin/products/odin-lite">Odin Lite</a> , which is technically more capable than the Pocket 3+ but less of a jump than its siblings. It&#39;s worth noting that AYN has a new “ <a data-i13n="cpos:46;pos:1" href="https://www.ayntec.com/">Loki</a> ” series of handhelds on the way as well. Nevertheless, the Odin is a standout among mobile gaming handhelds. You can read our full <a data-i13n="cpos:47;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ayn-odin-review-203045715.html">Odin Pro review</a> for more details.</p><h2> Another good (but pricey) option: Logitech G Cloud</h2><p><core-commerce id="b306417b5c9a40148fa9f3e6d66439dc" data-type="product-list"></p><p> If the <a data-i13n="cpos:48;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Mb2dpdGVjaC1IYW5kaGVsZC1Mb25nLUJhdHRlcnktVG91Y2hzY3JlZW4tTGlnaHR3ZWlnaHQtVGFibGV0L2RwL0IwOVQ5RkhaTEg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tenItMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImRmYzNlMGIzLWRhMjEtNDFlNi1iNGM4LTBmY2M0MTFlODZkZCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAARd6axxr2bgHu-7I91qbLJFtIEJP3Ffg-v0g4OWFuiuQ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLogitech-Handheld-Long-Battery-Touchscreen-Lightweight-Tablet%2Fdp%2FB09T9FHZLH">Logitech G Cloud</a> cost $150 or so less, it might be the best Android handheld on the market. Its 7-inch, 1080p display is bright, vibrant and altogether more pleasing to look at than the Retroid Pocket 3+, AYN Odin and even the entry-level Steam Deck. Despite having the same screen size as the Deck, it weighs a half pound less and its contoured grips are easy to hold for hours. Its haptics work as they should, and it gets a good 10 to 12 hours of battery life. The big panel makes it a treat for game streaming, and in terms of emulation, it can play into the Dreamcast/PSP range comfortably. Since Logitech is an established firm, you don&#39;t have to worry about extended shipping fees or wait times, either; just grab one from your retailer of choice and you&#39;ll have it in a few days.</p><p> Alas, the G Cloud has typically sold for $300 in recent months. While that&#39;s $50 less than its launch price, it&#39;s still too much when the Pocket 3+ and Odin get you most of the way there for much less, and when the Steam Deck can do far more for $100 extra. The Odin is more powerful, too; the G Cloud can still play some GameCube, 3DS and PS2 games, but not as comfortably, particularly at higher resolutions. Plus, while the G Cloud doesn&#39;t feel cheap, its triggers are somewhat shallow, and its face buttons are just OK. (The triggers are analog, though.) And because the device only supports the <a data-i13n="cpos:49;pos:1" href="https://www.howtogeek.com/235596/whats-the-difference-between-fat32-exfat-and-ntfs/">FAT32</a> file system, it can&#39;t play any games larger than 4GB off a microSD card. All that said, the G Cloud is still a more luxurious experience than the Odin and Pocket 3+ in many ways. If money is no object, or if you ever see on sale around $200, it&#39;s worth considering.</p><h2> A premium device for vintage portable games: Analogue Pocket</h2><p><core-commerce id="594b93114f04495a99ed1d15690924e7" data-type="product-list"></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:50;pos:1" href="https://store.analogue.co/#pocket">Analogue Pocket</a> is the ultimate Game Boy. As we note in <a data-i13n="cpos:51;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/analogue-pocket-review-150056011.html">our review</a> , its vertical design is built like a modernized version of Nintendo&#39;s classic handheld. The general layout is the same, and it can even work with classic accessories like the Game Boy Camera. But in contrast, it has four face buttons instead of two, a couple of triggers on the back, microSD and USB-C ports and a rechargeable battery rated for six to 10 hours of playtime. Most notably, there&#39;s a gorgeous 3.5-inch display that&#39;s backlit and incredibly sharp (615 ppi) but can look like an old Game Boy screen through different filter modes. This is an elegant handheld with a premium feel, plus it can output to a TV with an optional dock.</p><p> Unlike the retro handhelds mentioned above, the Pocket is designed to play actual cartridges, not just emulate ROM files. It can play Game Boy, Game Boy Color and Game Boy Advance games through its cartridge slot, with games from the Sega Game Gear (and eventually, other systems like the TurboGrafx-16 and Atari Lynx) playable through optional adapters. Like past Analogue devices, the Pocket uses field programmable gate array (FPGA) motherboards to mimic its target systems on a hardware level. In practice, this means the Pocket&#39;s “emulation” of older titles is near-perfect, with a level of responsiveness and visual faithfulness that software-based emulation can&#39;t match. Pop a Game Boy or GBA cartridge in here and you can essentially play it as nature intended.</p><p> That said, thanks to a <a data-i13n="cpos:52;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/analogue-pocket-openfpga-firmware-update-beta-pdp1-spacewar-150038571.html">big update</a> last year and an active community around the device, the Pocket can also run ROMs off a microSD card and <a data-i13n="cpos:53;pos:1" href="https://retrogamecorps.com/2022/08/07/analogue-pocket-jailbreak-guide/">thus play</a> systems like the SNES and Sega Genesis. At $220, the Pocket isn&#39;t cheap, and its shoulder buttons aren&#39;t as crisp to press as the excellent face buttons or d-pad. Still, if you have a collection of Game Boy, Game Gear or GBA games, the Pocket is the most luxurious way to play them, and it&#39;s only become more versatile since launch. Its biggest problem is that it&#39;s extremely hard to get — expect to wait <a data-i13n="cpos:54;pos:1" href="https://www.analogue.co/support/resource/pocket-preorder-faq">several months</a> for any new order to ship.</p><h2> A charming indie game machine: Playdate</h2><p><core-commerce id="a4e1de0dce834588bd6fdac9c6e8fe46" data-type="product-list"></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:55;pos:1" href="https://shop.play.date/#buy">Playdate</a> , from app developer and <a data-i13n="cpos:56;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-10-10-gaming-irl-untitled-goose-game.html"><em>Untitled Goose Game</em></a> <em>&nbsp;</em> publisher Panic, might be the most niche device in this guide. It&#39;s a tiny yellow box with a 2.7-inch monochrome display, two face buttons, a d-pad and a physical crank built into its side. <a data-i13n="cpos:57;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/playdate-review-indie-games-crank-170054294.html">Our review</a> called it a cross between a Game Boy and a business card, and it is indeed incredibly compact, measuring about three inches tall and just 0.18 pounds. Its game library largely consists of <a data-i13n="cpos:58;pos:1" href="https://play.date/games/">oddball indies</a> , most of which focus on one or two core ideas instead of stuffing in as many mechanics as possible. A couple dozen of those games come with the Playdate for no extra cost, a few others are available through a <a data-i13n="cpos:59;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/playdates-first-store-update-adds-four-games-and-a-calculator-210551529.html">built-in store</a> and hundreds more can be <a data-i13n="cpos:60;pos:1" href="https://help.play.date/games/sideloading/">sideloaded</a> from shops like <a data-i13n="cpos:61;pos:1" href="https://itch.io/games/tag-playdate">Itch.io</a> .</p><p> None of this is designed for emulation or capital-m “Modern” gaming, and at $200, it&#39;s wildly expensive given its limitations. Plus, while the display is smooth and sharp enough, it&#39;s not backlit, so it&#39;s difficult to view in dim lighting. But beyond that, the Playdate is as polished as it is adorable, and many of its games are simple fun. Battery life is decent at six to eight hours as well. In a sea of devices that try to be everything for everyone, the Playdate&#39;s goals are admirably focused and low-key. For the most part, it achieves them. If you&#39;re into smaller-scale games and have some cash to burn, it&#39;ll be a charming little toy. Like the Analogue Pocket, however, actually getting a hold of one will take some time: As of this writing, Panic says new Playdate orders won&#39;t ship until “late 2023.”</p><h2> Honorable mentions </h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-03/d24fa570-b9ce-11ed-9fcf-89b58257dcef" alt="在像《怒之铁拳 4》这样具有原生控制器支持的游戏中，Razer Edge 会自动检测，这使得设置变得极其简单。" data-uuid="6c0c02b5-4e31-30a2-822e-ddec51b16f7d"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Sam Rutherford/Engadget</div></figure><h3> Razer Edge</h3><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:62;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Razer;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=d043077a-4ba1-4321-a933-30b8701d8d31&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Razer&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJkMDQzMDc3YS00YmExLTQzMjEtYTkzMy0zMGI4NzAxZDhkMzEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucmF6ZXIuY29tL21vYmlsZS1oYW5kaGVsZHMvcmF6ZXItZWRnZSIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZGZjM2UwYjMtZGEyMS00MWU2LWI0YzgtMGZjYzQxMWU4NmRkIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAeLmAX1k3BL3dIGC9hN7md7Q9Rw5ojwl6iQCM-7ZERuk&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.razer.com%2Fmobile-handhelds%2Frazer-edge">Razer Edge</a> sits in a similar no man&#39;s land as the Logitech G Cloud. As we said in <a data-i13n="cpos:63;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/razer-edge-review-a-new-breed-of-gaming-handheld-170026147.html">our review</a> , the hardware isn&#39;t bad at all. It&#39;s about as powerful as a flagship phone from 2022, so it can play just about all Android games at max settings and emulate GameCube, PS2 and Wii games well. Its 144Hz OLED display is impressive, and both its speakers and battery life are solid.</p><p> But the design is odd: It&#39;s essentially a standalone tablet attached to a Razer Kishi V2, so it doesn&#39;t feel quite as stable as something like the AYN Odin or Logitech G Cloud. The display also has a superwide 20:9 aspect ratio that isn&#39;t well-suited to most retro games, so the effective screen space for emulation isn&#39;t much more than what you&#39;d get from a smaller device. It may be one of the more powerful Android handhelds, but at $400, the whole thing is way too expensive.</p><p><core-commerce id="048b19a69f414411befe4077a9c77307" data-type="product-list"></p><h3> Miyoo Mini+</h3><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:64;pos:1" href="https://powkiddy.com/products/miyoo-mini-plus-portable-retro-handheld-game-console-mini-ips-screen-linux-system-childrens-gift?variant=43779530391799">Miyoo Mini+</a> is more affordable than our top picks and comes in a well-built, Game Boy-style form factor that fits nicely with older games. Its 3.5-inch display really pops for something in the $70 to $80 range, its battery lasts as long as it needs to, and we found it to emulate retro consoles up to the PlayStation 1 without much issue. As a Linux handheld, its software is extensively customizable, though it can require a bit of tinkering to get the most out of it as a result.</p><p> Unfortunately, between stock shortages and its lack of availability at major retailers, the Mini+ has been difficult to actually buy. If you can&#39;t find one, <a data-i13n="cpos:65;pos:1" href="https://anbernic.com/products/rg35xx">Anbernic&#39;s RG35XX</a> should be a decent alternative; it&#39;s a bit easier to pick up and use once it&#39;s set up, though it lacks built-in WiFi. </p><p><core-commerce id="51d2dd22bffd49d6b7c6814fd038bc2d" data-type="product-list"></p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-01/e44f8410-7925-11ec-bcf6-da9b33ed53cc" alt="Backbone One" data-uuid="c2828a10-2452-3ef5-b4cf-3d52494fa829"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Mat Smith/ Engadget</div></figure><h3> Anbernic RG405M</h3><p> We weren&#39;t able to test it, but the <a data-i13n="cpos:66;pos:1" href="https://anbernic.com/products/rg405m">Anbernic RG405M</a> should be a good alternative to the Retroid Pocket 3+ for those who want something more compact. The two devices run on the same chipset, but the RG405M has a 4-inch display and a more substantial metal frame. Its 4:3 aspect ratio means you won&#39;t have to deal with black bars as much for retro games, too, though it can feel crunched with newer systems and cloud streaming. At $170 or so, it&#39;s also pricier than the Pocket 3+.</p><p><core-commerce id="8b9fe82fb3324dd1b568893a98b0f8e8" data-type="product-list"></p><h3> Backbone One</h3><p> At their core, all of the mobile handhelds we&#39;ve mentioned are just modified Android or Linux tablets. If you play more casually, you can get a similar experience by hooking up your existing smartphone to a mobile gamepad like the <a data-i13n="cpos:67;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfceEnSBS12tfYUPf4HoDQPg6H0kbEiYet1VLtezCk5X&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBackbone-One-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Android%2Fdp%2FB0BMD4KFSL">Backbone One</a> . This connects directly to your phone&#39;s USB-C or Lightning port and immediately works with any game with controller support. Its face buttons are somewhat noisy, and its d-pad is a bit spongy, but it&#39;s comfortable for its size and has all the inputs needed for modern gameplay, including analog triggers and clickable joysticks. There&#39;s also a headphone jack and pass-through charging port, plus a useful app for starting party chats. The One costs $100, which isn&#39;t cheap, but it feels <a data-i13n="cpos:68;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/backbone-one-ios-gamepad-review-143015385.html">much more natural</a> than using a console controller with a <a data-i13n="cpos:69;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATKUhZ2_rdudgQYaVveEijod6gKqgdSEtrTJibQTkJjD&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPowerA-Mobile-Gaming-Controllers-Android-x%2Fdp%2FB08NYGD5G9">clip</a> .</p><p><core-commerce id="cef2b38fffd24b09ae1d32cbc8837581" data-type="product-list"></p><p></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-handheld-gaming-system-140018863.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-handheld-gaming-system-140018863.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> dfc3e0b3-da21-41e6-b4c8-0fcc411e86dd</guid><dc:creator> Jeff Dunn</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 19:00:11 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687909491</ingested><modified> 2023-06-27T23:45:00+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jeff Dunn]]></category><media:content height="995" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/54f75770-fbe2-11ed-b844-614d7c270215" width="1700"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="995" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/54f75770-fbe2-11ed-b844-614d7c270215" width="1700"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A woman holds up a Steam Deck handheld console with the back of it facing the camera.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Steam Deck]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘Among Us’ cartoon coming from teams behind ‘Infinity Train’ and 'Star Trek: Lower Decks’]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Hit video game <em>Among Us</em> is getting the cartoon treatment,<ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://variety.com/2023/tv/news/among-us-animated-series-cbs-studios-owen-dennis-1235655516/">正如最初报道的</a></ins><ins><a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://variety.com/2023/tv/news/among-us-animated-series-cbs-studios-owen-dennis-1235655516/"><em>Variety.</em></a></ins> CBS Studios is behind the venture, partnering up with Innersloth, the game studio originally responsible for the indie sensation. There looks to be plenty of talent behind the scenes here, as the showrunner is Owen Dennis, the creator of the criminally-underrated <em>Infinity Train.</em> Titmouse Studios is handling the animation, after successful work on shows like <em>Star Trek: Lower Decks</em> and <em>Bigmouth.</em></p><p> If you are at all familiar with the game, the series description will seem like deja vu. The show will feature the crew of a spacecraft as they are murdered and replaced by an alien shapeshifter in an attempt to sabotage the ship and cause mass confusion. In other words, it&#39;s the game, only with professional voice actors instead of your friends and family.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> There&#39;s no voice cast yet, or even some simple still shots of the animation. There hasn&#39;t even been a streaming platform or network announced to house the cartoon, but with CBS Studios bankrolling, Paramount+ is a good bet. Though, Paramount+ has been doing that thing modern streamers do where they not only cancel shows<ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/star-trek-prodigy-will-be-pulled-from-paramount-next-week-191704393.html">but immediately delete them,</a></ins> so who knows.</p><p> Should you be excited for this animated series? Creator Owen Dennis cut his teeth on the critically acclaimed Cartoon Network series <em>Regular Show</em> before moving onto the<ins> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Wall Street Journal;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2f007401-3eaa-4237-b69b-54ccbe125502&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARKhfx291OmAYumsY52rVJK7Sq7aRY0fZURvmD2wGQ8i&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Finfinity-train-review-an-endless-ride-through-dreamlike-worlds-11564687906" class="rapid-with-clickid">absolutely stellar</a></ins><ins> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Wall Street Journal;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2f007401-3eaa-4237-b69b-54ccbe125502&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARKhfx291OmAYumsY52rVJK7Sq7aRY0fZURvmD2wGQ8i&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Finfinity-train-review-an-endless-ride-through-dreamlike-worlds-11564687906" class="rapid-with-clickid"><em>Infinity Train.</em></a></ins> Dennis served as showrunner throughout all four seasons of <em>Infinity Train</em> before it was, you&#39;ll never guess, canceled and then completely erased by Max. There&#39;s no official DVDs or Blu-Rays, but you can purchase the episodes digitally via Amazon and Apple to see what all the fuss is about.</p><p> In the meantime, the <em>Among Us</em> series has no release date, though the show is covered by The Animation Guild and not the WGA, so work should be able to proceed without crossing picket lines.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/among-us-cartoon-coming-from-teams-behind-infinity-train-and-star-trek-lower-decks-184059395.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/among-us-cartoon-coming-from-teams-behind-infinity-train-and-star-trek-lower-decks-184059395.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ffa3187e-445b-453e-a1ad-52f3f4fef8d8</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 18:40:59 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687890547</ingested><modified> 2023-06-27T18:29:11+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Visual Arts]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Humanities]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1120" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/817614c0-1515-11ee-bb9d-81c549971453" width="1996"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1120" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/817614c0-1515-11ee-bb9d-81c549971453" width="1996"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Innersloth]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[An image of the 'Among Us' red dude giving the shushing finger sign.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Among Us Cartoon ]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple has posted the entire first episode of ‘Silo’ on Twitter]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> A